                      "kind": "text",
                      "text": "The eigenvalues, each repeated according to its multiplicity.\nThe eigenvalues are not necessarily ordered. The resulting\narray will be of complex type, unless the imaginary part is\nzero in which case it will be cast to a real type. When "
